            <description><![CDATA[<p>Release date: 2026-05-21</p>
<h2 id="new">New</h2>
<h2 id="improvements">Improvements</h2>
<h2 id="bug-fixes">Bug Fixes</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>Fixed startup for some self-managed license users.</strong>
NameQuick now opens the right license repair screen instead of getting
stuck on “Checking license” when a paid self-managed license needs
device access repaired.</li>
<li><strong>Improved repair guidance for self-managed licenses.</strong>
When a license reaches its device limit, NameQuick now keeps the account
correctly recognized as self-managed and shows the right recovery
actions.</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
